translate ru EscapeVoid3_5716acae:
    # "Every part of her wanted to escape, but there was still hope."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_17e3f5a9:
    # "If only she could bring them to listen. If only she could speak the right words."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_76b09f43:
    # "As the tendrils kept her jaw spread, more reached into her."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_5c86d192:
    # "Into her mouth."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_4fb10149:
    # "Her throat."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_15dabc4c:
    # "Between her legs."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_a5451292:
    # "Entering her from behind."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_6bcb2dd0:
    # "Her nose. Ears. Eyes."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_23b42001:
    # "Every part of her body became an entrance for the void tendrils, and it spared her nothing."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_dbcd6eb7:
    # "Sarah felt all of it, spreading within her."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_030a1acb:
    # "Her spasms at the pain, contained by the titanic grip that the tendrils held on every part of her body."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_97cf6898:
    # "Speak!"
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_074e9a05:
    # "She tried to command herself, but she could not speak anymore."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_f1219f75:
    # "Nor would the thing listen."
    ""

translate ru EscapeVoid3_38d71131:
    # "It was meaningless to resist much longer."
    ""

